      • addChart

        private void addChart​(java.lang.String id,
                      java.lang.String title,
                      java.lang.String xLabel,
                      java.lang.String yLabel,
                      java.util.ArrayList<Statistic> statistics,
                      java.lang.Boolean updateDaily,
                      boolean doubleChart)
        Adds one new chart to the ChartList with multiple statistics.
        Parameters:
        id - the id of the chart.
        title - the title of the chart.
        xLabel - the label that will be displayed on the x axis of the chart.
        yLabel - the label that will be displayed on the y axis of the chart.
        statistics - the Statistic object that will be linked to the chart.
        updateDaily - makes the chart add a data point once every 24 hours instead of once every hour.
        doubleChart - if the chart should have double width.
